## Vite env vars must be prefixed with `VITE_`
##
## IMPORTANT:
## If your frontend is served over HTTPS (e.g. AWS Amplify), your API must also be HTTPS
## (or be behind an HTTPS proxy like CloudFront / API Gateway / ALB).
##
## Example:
VITE_API_BASE=https://api.example.com/api

## If you have a reverse proxy that forwards your site’s `/api` to the backend:
# VITE_API_BASE=/api

## Optional: Mobile app download links shown on About page
## - Android: direct APK URL (same-origin `/downloads/...` also works)
## - iOS: App Store / TestFlight / website URL
# VITE_ANDROID_APK_URL=https://example.com/downloads/haappii-billing.apk
# VITE_IOS_APP_URL=https://example.com/ios
